title: Boogarins - As Plantas Que Curam (2013 - EP) 320K
description:
Boogarins - As Plantas Que Curam FULL EP 320K



A modern revival of 60's Tropicalism movement takes part of the Brazilian independent scene in As Plantas Que Curam.  Achieving high scores at critics all around the world, this album is a must-listen to the lovers of psychedelic culture and music in general. With its philosophical lyrics, As Plantas Que Curam may lead you to profound and questioning thoughts. But isn't that what psychodelic rock is all about?
